## 🚀 COMANDOS DE CONTROL

### Iniciar Agentes
```bash
smarter-mcp start --all
smarter-mcp start sales-agent
smarter-mcp start lab-agent --verbose
```

### Detener Agentes
```bash
smarter-mcp stop --all
smarter-mcp stop support-agent
```

### Ver Estado
```bash
smarter-mcp status
smarter-mcp logs --agent=sales --tail=100
smarter-mcp metrics --period=week
```

### Forzar Ejecución
```bash
smarter-mcp trigger sales-agent --now
smarter-mcp trigger lab-agent --optimize-routes
```

